nodes.text: Star Wars: The Clone Wars: Incredible Vehicles

Star Wars: The Clone Wars: Incredible Vehicles is a reference guide on the vehicles in the Star Wars: The Clone Wars television series, released on August 15, 2011 in the US and September 1, 2011 in the UK. Modeled after Dorling Kindersley's Star Wars: Incredible Cross-Sections series, it features eight cross-sections of starships and vehicles. The book has 127 pages. The guide was written by Jason Fry and illustrated by Richard Chasemore.
